   `SYNOPSIS`
-       `git-mailz` [-f *ENVELOPE-SENDER*] [*FILE*|*DIRECTORY*]
+       `git-mailz` [-f *ENVELOPE-SENDER*] [*FILE* | *DIRECTORY*]...
 
   `DESCRIPTION`
-       Feeds patches given on the command line to sendmail(1).
+       Feeds patches given on the command line to *sendmail(1)*.
        Arguments can name individual patch files or directories,
