-       environment variables used by git(1), zsh(1), possibly others.
+       which do use them.  This means `git-mailz` may be influenced by
+       environment variables used by *git(1)*, *zsh(1)*, possibly others.
 
   `DIAGNOSTICS`
-       The git-mailz utility exits 0 on success, and >0 if an error occurs.
+       The `git-mailz` utility exits 0 on success, and >0 if an error occurs.
 
